                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Solid-state   detector   telescope",
                " which comprised two DSSSDs  (double-sided  Si  strip",
                " delta-E detector) and HpGe detector,  which measured",
                " proton emission angle and energies, respectively."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coaxial HpGe detector that had a relative peak",
                " efficiency of  70  %  for  the detection of 1.33 MeV",
                " gamma-rays, placed  with the front face 70  mm  from",
                " the  target  at  an angle  of  95 degree to the beam",
                " direction and subtended a solid angle of ~ 700 msr."
              ]
            }
          ],
